   CORTEX Trust Engine
        â”œâ”€â”€ SHA-256 hash-chained ledger
        â”œâ”€â”€ Merkle tree checkpoints
        â”œâ”€â”€ Reputation-weighted consensus
        â””â”€â”€ EU AI Act compliance reports
```

